%h1
  Mindapples in universities

%p
  We believe that Mindapples has strong applications into the world of student and graduate wellbeing. In particular, we are keen to support people who are in transition into adult life, and also who are struggling to find work after leaving university.

%h2
  Our approach

%p
  All our programmes are based on the core Mindapples Self-Observation Process:
